					<header>
						<h2>Who I am</h2>
					</header>
					<figure><img src="./images/photo_mumbai.jpg" alt=""  style="float: right; padding: 0px 0px 1px 10px; max-width:50%;"></figure>
					<p align="justify">I'm Sarthak Parui, pursuing M.S. by Research under the guidance of <a href="http://www.cse.iitm.ac.in/~amittal/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Dr. Anurag Mittal</a> at <a href="http://www.iitm.ac.in/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">IIT Madras.</a> Currently, I am in 5th semester of M.S program with CGPA 9.33/10. </p>
					
							<p align="justify">My area of research is Computer Vision and I work on Shape-based Image Matching and Large Scale Image Retrieval.</p>
							
							<!-- <p>"There are two ways of constructing a software design. One way is to make it so simple that there are obviously no deficiencies. And the other way is to make it so complicated that there are no obvious deficiencies." </p> -->
							
							
							
							<p align="justify">Before joining IIT Madras, I was associated with <a href="http://www.tcs.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tata Consultancy Services.</a> for 1 year 9 months. My main area of hands-on experience has been analysis and coding in Web and Mobile domains.</p>
							<p align="justify">For more details, please have a look at my <a href="./docs/resume-sarthak.pdf" target="blank">CV</a>.</p>
					
				</div>
